usage: somethinglike.py [-h] [-n NUMBER] [-r] movie_title [movie_title ...]

positional arguments:
  movie_title           the title of a movie you like

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -n NUMBER, --number NUMBER
                        number of recommendations to display (default: 3)
  -r, --random          randomize the results
